task_details.description: Use a Semantic SLAM algorithm to construct an object map of the environment. An object map describes each object with a probabilistic label suggestion, spatial location, and optional probabilistic state change suggestion. This task provides passive robot control, and sensor observations with ground truth robot pose.
task_details.name: semantic_slam:passive:ground_truth

environment_details.description:
Mini room environment with all of the base objects in their normal place.
All of the other mini room environments are based off this with any combination
of objects, object positions, & lighting changed
environment_details.name: miniroom
